description:
This is a 20 minute workout called '20 Minute Full Body Workout At Home - No Equipment' from the channel Roberta's Gym.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: During this pandemic, we are all susceptible to weight gain. Since we can't go for a run or to the gym and we're stuck at home, it's easy to get sucked in to a cycle of eating, watching, sleeping. If you add working out into the chemistry, then you stand a chance at having a healthy and fit body despite having no chance to go out of the house!

These exercises can be done at home and they're all body-weight so there's no need to use any equipment. All you need is your body and your devices (mobile, laptop, TV) to get this party started!

Today's 20-min full body workout guarantees weight loss results in no time. With discipline and a healthy diet, this workout will give you an amazing figure and a healthy body even during quarantine.
